    "source": "Altimetry: Error (mission id ers2 not in select statement), Snow depth: Monthly climatology based on regional merging of Warren Climatology with 50% reduction for first-year sea ice in the central Arctic and AMSR-2 based snow depth from IUP Bremen in remaining ice-covered regions, Mean Sea Surface: DTU21 global mean sea surface, Sea ice Concentration: C3S Sea Ice Concentration CDR/ICDR v3.0, Sea ice type: C3S Sea Ice Type CDR/ICDR v3.0, Region code: NSIDC regional mask for Arctic sea ice trends and climatologies (J. Scott Stewart and Walter N. Meier (2021), NSIDC)",
